title: The Artie Quitter Podcast SEP 25 2015 Fri (Best Of).mp3
description:
After quitting the "Howard Stern Show," surviving a suicide attempt and hosting his own DirecTV program, comedian Artie Lange is venturing into a new frontier -- podcasting.
Regular Co-Hosts for Artie include Comedians Joe Matarese, Geno Bisconte, Sue Costello, Chris Cotton, Stacey Prussman & Mike Bocchetti, which add to the vibe of hanging out with the guys -- talkin' sports and bustin' chops.
